channel.title: I really need help for webclient!
channel.description:
Hey guys! Well I know I've posted about this before but I [b]REALLY[/b] need help with making my Webclient.
In my other posts some people have a [b]LITTLE BIT[/b] help me out but not the whole way I have hundreds of people to please.
I've made a downloadable client before but not a Webclient. I've followed tutorials. I've Jared some files. When I just have my HTML page about it, it just can't download the cache files!
Thanks for your help guys! -Nameme123
P.S - Lets just hope that this time I actually can get an answer for all this.
